{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">WELCOME TO MY ADVENTURE BOOK</h2>Before us are the exciting adventures of Jack, who went to the library and discovered a magic book. Having opened it, he finds himself in a wonderful world where he has to solve riddles. Find objects, solve puzzles and help the local inhabitants of this world so that you can return home.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825390/extras/mab_banner_1.gif?t=1733772760\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Main features</h2>We have added several visual styles for this game. You can switch from one style to another at any time and look at the game world with a new perspective.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825390/extras/mab_styles.png?t=1733772760\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DLC for this game</h2>If you liked the game and want to support our work financially.<br>You can purchase the DLC, which will contain additional reskins for this game.<br>We will replenish them with your help.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825390/extras/mab_dlc.png?t=1733772760\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">My Adventure Book 2</h2>If enough funds come in, we will develop a continuation of My Adventure Book 2. Which is much larger, brighter and with more elaborate mini-games.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825390/extras/mab2_banner.gif?t=1733772760\" />","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2825390?t=1733772760","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825390/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1733772760","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825390/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733772760","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2